review_text: Super petit park but considering it is in the middle of residential buildings, businesses, it certainly fill a nice void that is quite popular.
A welcoming oasis in the middle of a vibrant local shopping area

(Translated by Google) I frequented this little corner all winter, I nicknamed it "My placotoir"! Now, with good weather, you should think about installing parasols, otherwise it will be too hot. And also see to find a way to prevent the grass from growing through the wood floor.

(Original)
J'ai fréquenté ce petit coin tout l 'hiver, je l'ai surnommé "Mon placotoir "!  Maintenant,  avec le beau temps, faudrait penser à y installer des parasols, sinon il y fera trop chaud.  Et aussi voir â trouver le moyen d'empêcher le gazon de pousser au travers du plancher de bois
